title: Ousama Ranking (Ranking of Kings)
synopsis: The web manga centers around Bojji, a deaf, powerless prince who cannot even wield a children's sword. As the firstborn son, he strives hard and dreams of becoming the world's greatest king. However, people mutter about him behind his back as "a good-for-nothing prince" and "no way he can be king."
voices: ['Hinata, Minami', 'Murase, Ayumu', 'Satou, Rina', 'Yasumoto, Hiroki', 'Yamashita, Daiki', 'Ueda, Youji', 'Miyake, Kenta', 'Sakamoto, Maaya', 'Sakurai, Takahiro', 'Shimoyama, Yoshimitsu']
